text: Ivan Diaconu is a ten-time national champion from Moldova who competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney.Olympic dreams come true for Port Alberni wrestler ==References== Category:Wrestlers at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Moldovan male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Moldova Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
